Notebook[{

Cell[CellGroupData[{
Cell["\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Cadena de favores\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]", \
"Title",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.948466334691944*^9, 
  3.948466337640871*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"e05f1020-d91d-aa4e-9b48-\
f49ec187af1e"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "En la pel\[IAcute]cula (y el libro) \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]cadena de \
favores\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote], plantean la siguiente estrategia para hacer \
m\[AAcute]s agradable a la comunidad: si alguien te hace un favor, en lugar \
de regresar el favor para que la cuenta quede saldada, haces favores (que no \
pudieran hacer elles mismes) a otras tres personas (diferentes a quien te \
ayud\[OAcute] en primera instancia). La idea es que haya un efecto domin\
\[OAcute] donde la gente se ayuda sin esperar algo a cambio.\n\nPodemos \
modelar este problema como un sistema din\[AAcute]mico para poder determinar:\
\n1) Bajo qu\[EAcute] condiciones la gente termina olvidando el movimiento.\n\
2) Bajo qu\[EAcute] condiciones el movimiento podr\[IAcute]a sobrevivir.\n3) \
La fracci\[OAcute]n de la poblaci\[OAcute]n que participa en el movimiento si \
\[EAcute]ste sobrevive.\n4) Cu\[AAcute]l es la cantidad m\[IAcute]nima de \
personas que deben iniciar el movimiento.\n\nComo hablamos de \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]supervivencia\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] y \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]poblaciones\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote], podemos modelar \
este movimiento mediante una ecuaci\[OAcute]n diferencial, igual que en din\
\[AAcute]mica de poblaciones. El modelo sugerido es el siguiente:\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         OverscriptBox[
          StyleBox["N", "TI"], "."], "\[LongEqual]", 
         StyleBox["c", "TI"], 
         RowBox[{"(", 
           StyleBox["N", "TI"], ")"}], 
         StyleBox["N", "TI"], 
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{
            StyleBox["P", "TI"], "-", 
            StyleBox["N", "TI"]}], 
          StyleBox["P", "TI"]], "-", "\[Mu]", 
         StyleBox["N", "TI"]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "\\dot{N}=c(N)N\\frac{P-N}{P}-\\mu N", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "e5fe6580-c69d-ea46-98f5-ad5f4281116b"],
 "\ndonde ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       StyleBox["N", "TI"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> "N", 
     "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "dd05250d-b70e-1b49-99e2-48760d7a3313"],
 " es el n\[UAcute]mero de personas que participan en el movimiento, y ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       StyleBox["P", "TI"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> "P", 
     "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "88fd3d50-73e0-2847-89de-aea0a3c749fa"],
 " es la poblaci\[OAcute]n total, que supondremos constante. Podemos \
interpretar cada uno de los t\[EAcute]rminos para entender cuales son las \
suposiciones del modelo:\n1) ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"-", 
    TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
        RowBox[{"\[Mu]", 
          StyleBox["N", "TI"]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
      "\\mu N", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
     "TeXAssistantTemplate"]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "d809140a-e23d-3f4d-8111-6c9030b860b7"],
 " es un t\[EAcute]rmino de disminuci\[OAcute]n. Modela el hecho de que \
eventualmente las personas se olvidan del movimiento. Supone una tasa de \
olvido constante ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|
    "boxes" -> FormBox["\[Mu]", TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "\\mu", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "16294e41-cc66-7841-86a9-852f5ef3585f"],
 ".\n2) ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       FractionBox[
        RowBox[{
          StyleBox["P", "TI"], "-", 
          StyleBox["N", "TI"]}], 
        StyleBox["P", "TI"]], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "\\frac{P-N}{P}", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "c1254d40-d580-6c43-83aa-52f96864fcea"],
 " es la fracci\[OAcute]n de la poblaci\[OAcute]n total que NO est\[AAcute] \
en el movimiento.\n3) ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       StyleBox["N", "TI"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> "N", 
     "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "9e8b9a3a-6683-7c4a-8238-3f63f7be421a"],
 " es el n\[UAcute]mero de personas que S\[CapitalIAcute] est\[AAcute] en el \
movimiento.\n4) ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["c", "TI"], "(", 
         StyleBox["N", "TI"], ")"}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "c(N)", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "30302e87-fb1f-714d-9b5b-8b48e87b0b7b"],
 " es la tasa de convencimiento per c\[AAcute]pita.\nEste modelo tambi\
\[EAcute]n es muy similar a los modelos epidemiol\[OAcute]gicos, as\[IAcute] \
que el primer t\[EAcute]rmino, que es el m\[AAcute]s complicado, lo podemos \
interpretar haciendo un s\[IAcute]mil epidemiol\[OAcute]gico. ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["N", "TI"], 
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{
            StyleBox["P", "TI"], "-", 
            StyleBox["N", "TI"]}], 
          StyleBox["P", "TI"]]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "N\\frac{P-N}{P}", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "09fa6499-3475-5b4b-acc4-5c0ac0b7ff64"],
 " representa el n\[UAcute]mero de encuentros exitosos entre personas en el \
movimiento con personas fuera del movimiento (excluye contactos entre dos \
personas fuera y entre dos personas dentro del movimiento), similar a los \
contactos entre sanos e infectados. El t\[EAcute]rmino ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["c", "TI"], "(", 
         StyleBox["N", "TI"], ")"}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "c(N)", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "a28f383b-f26b-284a-9450-e19fdb0448a9"],
 " es an\[AAcute]logo a la infectividad, que mide la probabilidad con la que \
estos encuentros resultan en la persona fuera del movimiento convencida en \
participar en \[EAcute]l. A diferencia de los modelos \
epidemiol\[OAcute]gicos, esta cantidad no es constante, sino que es una funci\
\[OAcute]n de ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       StyleBox["N", "TI"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> "N", 
     "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "510d4918-ab3a-4446-ba34-45fb55059e21"],
 ", pues suponemos que mientras m\[AAcute]s personas haya en el movimiento, m\
\[AAcute]s familiar estar\[AAcute] la persona a convencer con el movimiento, \
y m\[AAcute]s f\[AAcute]cil su convencimiento.\n\nDado que ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["c", "TI"], "(", 
         StyleBox["N", "TI"], ")"}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "c(N)", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "bbb1d3eb-0531-7d42-ba34-fd8e12eb70e0"],
 " es una probabilidad, su crecimiento debe estar acotado. Para tomar en \
cuenta esta restricci\[OAcute]n, se consideran dos funciones que muestran el \
fen\[OAcute]meno de \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]saturaci\[OAcute]n\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote], donde ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["c", "TI"], "(", 
         StyleBox["N", "TI"], ")"}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "c(N)", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "3d8936eb-24df-3a44-ac69-327a3e053c3e"],
 " crece con ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       StyleBox["N", "TI"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> "N", 
     "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "6570f926-8065-f841-ae59-550139ed59d4"],
 " hasta mantenerse casi constante en un valor l\[IAcute]mite. Haremos el an\
\[AAcute]lisis con cada una de estas formas funcionales de ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["c", "TI"], "(", 
         StyleBox["N", "TI"], ")"}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "c(N)", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "99794db7-e5be-664a-beaf-cdb9f6069aaf"],
 "."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9484738340947056`*^9, 3.9484739793651543`*^9}, {
   3.9484741679920197`*^9, 3.948474417450218*^9}, {3.948474453599861*^9, 
   3.9484744558335896`*^9}, {3.9484745181735497`*^9, 3.948474562264456*^9}, {
   3.9484746383674126`*^9, 3.948474765499668*^9}, {3.948474830760538*^9, 
   3.9484749123280277`*^9}, {3.948480655702276*^9, 3.9484809426770973`*^9}, {
   3.9484811193715706`*^9, 3.9484812759715614`*^9}, 
   3.9484815962878647`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"9c7e3630-e6c7-044c-91a6-\
2c53847cd847"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Primera forma", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9484813050186424`*^9, 
  3.9484813070271263`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"c2d1d5ac-1a93-9a42-8f41-\
83619f2f2df2"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "En primera instancia, consideramos la forma funcional\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["c", "TI"], 
         RowBox[{"(", 
           StyleBox["N", "TI"], ")"}], "\[LongEqual]", "\[Alpha]", 
         FractionBox[
          StyleBox["N", "TI"], 
          RowBox[{
            StyleBox["A", "TI"], "+", 
            StyleBox["N", "TI"]}]]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "c(N)=\\alpha\\frac{N}{A+N}", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "5d9d6442-bed7-1e4c-8f5f-a69414c3c7cd"],
 ",\ndonde ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|
    "boxes" -> FormBox["\[Alpha]", TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "\\alpha", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "a40e49ac-d530-4041-800b-788cab86601d"],
 " y ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       StyleBox["A", "TI"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> "A", 
     "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "dc31d936-2559-1b42-a693-a9b20afd73b1"],
 " sson constantes positivas. F\[AAcute]cilmente, vemos que ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         UnderscriptBox["lim", 
          RowBox[{
            StyleBox["N", "TI"], "\[Rule]", "\[Infinity]"}], 
          LimitsPositioning -> True], 
         StyleBox["c", "TI"], 
         RowBox[{"(", 
           StyleBox["N", "TI"], ")"}], "\[LongEqual]", "\[Alpha]"}], 
       TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "\\lim_{N\\rightarrow\\infty}c(N)=\\alpha", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "9ebe1784-b54f-1749-97b7-e447f5425537"],
 ", por lo que ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|
    "boxes" -> FormBox["\[Alpha]", TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "\\alpha", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "31d0a358-4fb3-234e-817e-74d546678321"],
 " es el supremo de los posibles valores de ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["c", "TI"], "(", 
         StyleBox["N", "TI"], ")"}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "c(N)", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "7c5274fa-2925-dc43-ad23-2e8c8111ef76"],
 ", lo cual modela la susceptibilidad innata de la gente a ser convencida. \
Adicionalmente, vemos que ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["c", "TI"], 
         RowBox[{"(", 
           StyleBox["A", "TI"], ")"}], "\[LongEqual]", 
         FractionBox["\[Alpha]", "2"]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "c(A)=\\frac{\\alpha}{2}", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "c68eab96-7d20-5346-be19-1f2f492ad63a"],
 ", por lo que ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       StyleBox["A", "TI"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> "A", 
     "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "b3c94ad3-4ee3-8340-b704-d51284c87f8b"],
 " es el n\[UAcute]mero de personas necesarias en el movimiento para que la \
probabilidad de convencimiento alcance la mitad de su valor m\[AAcute]ximo. \
Por lo tanto, si ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       StyleBox["A", "TI"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> "A", 
     "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "8a062374-f17c-de4d-b77c-9432fc5e28fc"],
 " es peque\[NTilde]o, es f\[AAcute]cil convencer a la gente a\[UAcute]n con \
pocas personas participando al movimiento, mientras que si ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       StyleBox["A", "TI"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> "A", 
     "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "4d1c35a9-8a62-ae41-8016-1b8467e7ea21"],
 " es grande, es dif\[IAcute]cil convencer a las personas a menos de que el \
movimiento sea considerablemente grande."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9484813181548996`*^9, 3.948481344167824*^9}, {
  3.9484813783431454`*^9, 3.948481521831915*^9}, {3.948481563122278*^9, 
  3.948481730194803*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"4318a56b-dbeb-6646-b3be-\
ac2a07b28b4e"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"Show", "[", 
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"Plot", "[", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"x", "/", 
      RowBox[{"(", 
       RowBox[{"5", "+", "x"}], ")"}]}], ",", 
     RowBox[{"{", 
      RowBox[{"x", ",", "0", ",", "20"}], "}"}], ",", 
     RowBox[{"AxesLabel", "->", 
      RowBox[{"{", 
       RowBox[{"\"\<N\>\"", ",", 
        RowBox[{"c", "[", "\"\<N\>\"", "]"}]}], "}"}]}], ",", 
     RowBox[{"PlotRange", "->", "All"}], ",", 
     RowBox[{"Ticks", "->", 
      RowBox[{"{", 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"{", 
         RowBox[{"{", 
          RowBox[{"5", ",", "A"}], "}"}], "}"}], ",", 
        RowBox[{"{", 
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"{", 
           RowBox[{"0.5", ",", 
            RowBox[{"0.5", "\[Alpha]"}]}], "}"}], ",", 
          RowBox[{"{", 
           RowBox[{"1", ",", "\[Alpha]"}], "}"}]}], "}"}]}], "}"}]}], ",", 
     RowBox[{"Epilog", "->", 
      RowBox[{"{", 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"Directive", "[", 
         RowBox[{"{", 
          RowBox[{"Red", ",", "Dashed"}], "}"}], "]"}], ",", 
        RowBox[{"Line", "[", 
         RowBox[{"{", 
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{"{", 
            RowBox[{"5", ",", "0"}], "}"}], ",", 
           RowBox[{"{", 
            RowBox[{"5", ",", "0.5"}], "}"}]}], "}"}], "]"}]}], "}"}]}]}], 
    "]"}], ",", 
   RowBox[{"Plot", "[", 
    RowBox[{"1", ",", 
     RowBox[{"{", 
      RowBox[{"x", ",", "0", ",", "20"}], "}"}], ",", 
     RowBox[{"PlotStyle", "->", 
      RowBox[{"{", 
       RowBox[{"Red", ",", "Dashed"}], "}"}]}]}], "]"}], ",", 
   RowBox[{"Plot", "[", 
    RowBox[{"0.5", ",", 
     RowBox[{"{", 
      RowBox[{"x", ",", "0", ",", "5"}], "}"}], ",", 
     RowBox[{"PlotStyle", "->", 
      RowBox[{"{", 
       RowBox[{"Red", ",", "Dashed"}], "}"}]}]}], "]"}]}], "]"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.948482172030918*^9, 3.9484821919171486`*^9}, {
   3.9484822248540783`*^9, 3.9484822682558346`*^9}, {3.948482329687977*^9, 
   3.9484823788526707`*^9}, {3.9484824499195766`*^9, 3.9484824548675976`*^9}, 
   3.9484825261113586`*^9, {3.948482583458914*^9, 3.948482655280531*^9}, {
   3.9484827031937504`*^9, 3.9484827893196926`*^9}, {3.9484829192524605`*^9, 
   3.948482937783249*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[11]:=",ExpressionUUID->"a676e5f3-0210-904c-b959-5907dbf386a5"],

