Cell[TextData[{
 "En este caso, tenemos la ecuaci\[OAcute]n diferencial ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         OverscriptBox[
          StyleBox["N", "TI"], "."], "\[LongEqual]", 
         StyleBox["f", "TI"], 
         RowBox[{"(", 
           StyleBox["N", "TI"], ")"}]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "\\dot{N}=f(N)", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "19b31f66-9d98-8242-b31a-3284abdb1a39"],
 ", donde\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["f", "TI"], 
         RowBox[{"(", 
           StyleBox["N", "TI"], ")"}], "\[LongEqual]", 
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{"\[Alpha]", 
            StyleBox["N", "TI"]}], 
          RowBox[{
            StyleBox["N", "TI"], "+", 
            StyleBox["A", "TI"]}]], 
         StyleBox["N", "TI"], 
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{
            StyleBox["P", "TI"], "-", 
            StyleBox["N", "TI"]}], 
          StyleBox["P", "TI"]], "-", "\[Mu]", 
         StyleBox["N", "TI"]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "f(N)=\\frac{\\alpha N}{N+A}N\\frac{P-N}{P}-\\mu N", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "b2fbe72b-03bf-c741-a38b-d1d906edbc19"],
 "\nPra responder las preguntas que hicimos antes, hacemos el \
an\[AAcute]lisis de estabilidad. Empezamos calculando las soluciones de \
equilibrio:\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["f", "TI"], 
         RowBox[{"(", 
           SuperscriptBox[
            StyleBox["N", "TI"], "*"], ")"}], "\[LongEqual]", 
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{"\[Alpha]", 
            SuperscriptBox[
             StyleBox["N", "TI"], "*"]}], 
          RowBox[{
            SuperscriptBox[
             StyleBox["N", "TI"], "*"], "+", 
            StyleBox["A", "TI"]}]], 
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["N", "TI"], "*"], 
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{
            StyleBox["P", "TI"], "-", 
            SuperscriptBox[
             StyleBox["N", "TI"], "*"]}], 
          StyleBox["P", "TI"]], "-", "\[Mu]", 
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["N", "TI"], "*"], "\[LongEqual]", "0"}], TraditionalForm], 
     "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "f(N^*)=\\frac{\\alpha N^*}{N^*+A}N^*\\frac{P-N^*}{P}-\\mu N^*=0", 
     "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "631e6e2c-48d4-7941-9fdd-b27d68b05090"],
 "\nAutom\[AAcute]ticamente vemos que ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SubsuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["N", "TI"], "1", "*"], "\[LongEqual]", "0"}], 
       TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> "N_1^*=0", "state" -> 
     "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "15e7b72b-f7f6-1d48-b6c9-38003d84f183"],
 " es una soluci\[OAcute]n de equilibrio. Dejando de lado esta \
soluci\[OAcute]n, las dem\[AAcute]s soluciones de equilibrio deben cumplir:\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{"\[Alpha]", 
            SuperscriptBox[
             StyleBox["N", "TI"], "*"]}], 
          RowBox[{
            SuperscriptBox[
             StyleBox["N", "TI"], "*"], "+", 
            StyleBox["A", "TI"]}]], 
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{
            StyleBox["P", "TI"], "-", 
            SuperscriptBox[
             StyleBox["N", "TI"], "*"]}], 
          StyleBox["P", "TI"]], "-", "\[Mu]", "\[LongEqual]", "0"}], 
       TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "\\frac{\\alpha N^*}{N^*+A}\\frac{P-N^*}{P}-\\mu =0", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "9f0a202e-7d7f-3b44-8368-f8f5ddf30437"],
 "\nMultiplicando en todos lados por ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["P", "TI"], "(", 
         RowBox[{
           SuperscriptBox[
            StyleBox["N", "TI"], "*"], "+", 
           StyleBox["A", "TI"]}], ")"}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "P(N^*+A)", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "0a9e7ceb-cf30-ce43-b0dc-bb472f2273e4"],
 " y haciendo un poco de \[AAcute]lgebra, llegamos a la ecuaci\[OAcute]n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["N", "TI"], "*2"], "+", 
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{"\[Mu]", 
            StyleBox["P", "TI"]}], "\[Alpha]"], 
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["N", "TI"], "*"], "+", 
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{"\[Mu]", 
            StyleBox["P", "TI"], 
            StyleBox["A", "TI"]}], "\[Alpha]"], "\[LongEqual]", "0"}], 
       TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "N^{*2}+\\frac{\\mu P}{\\alpha}N^*+\\frac{\\mu PA}{\\alpha}=0", "state" -> 
     "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "da792be2-cdd4-1d45-bc42-abf5982064dc"],
 ", \nla cual podemos usar con la f\[OAcute]rmula cuadr\[AAcute]tica, \
obteniendo\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SubsuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["N", "TI"], 
          RowBox[{"2", ",", "3"}], "*"], "\[LongEqual]", 
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{
            StyleBox["P", "TI"], "-", 
            FractionBox[
             RowBox[{"\[Mu]", 
               StyleBox["P", "TI"]}], "\[Alpha]"], "\[PlusMinus]", 
            SqrtBox[
             RowBox[{
               SuperscriptBox[
                RowBox[{"(", 
                  RowBox[{
                    FractionBox[
                    RowBox[{"\[Mu]", 
                    StyleBox["P", "TI"]}], "\[Alpha]"], "-", 
                    StyleBox["P", "TI"]}], ")"}], "2"], "-", "4", 
               FractionBox[
                RowBox[{"\[Mu]", 
                  StyleBox["P", "TI"], 
                  StyleBox["A", "TI"]}], "\[Alpha]"]}]]}], "2"]}], 
       TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "N_{2,3}^*=\\frac{P-\\frac{\\mu P}{\\alpha}\\pm\\sqrt{(\\frac{\\mu \
P}{\\alpha}-P)^2-4\\frac{\\mu PA}{\\alpha}}}{2}", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "e86bb4a2-c40a-4d47-997b-0b06e6a8cf99"],
 "\nDe inmediato vemos que las soluciones no son reales, es decir, no existen \
si\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SuperscriptBox[
          RowBox[{"(", 
            RowBox[{
              FractionBox[
               RowBox[{"\[Mu]", 
                 StyleBox["P", "TI"]}], "\[Alpha]"], "-", 
              StyleBox["P", "TI"]}], ")"}], "2"], "-", "4", 
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{"\[Mu]", 
            StyleBox["P", "TI"], 
            StyleBox["A", "TI"]}], "\[Alpha]"], "<", "0"}], TraditionalForm], 
     "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "(\\frac{\\mu P}{\\alpha}-P)^2-4\\frac{\\mu PA}{\\alpha}}<0", "state" -> 
     "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "cfc3cf35-930a-7a48-934e-c60e835a6324"],
 ",\ny las dos soluciones se fusionan y son iguales a ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SubsuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["N", "TI"], 
          RowBox[{"2", ",", "3"}], "*"], "\[LongEqual]", 
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{"\[Alpha]", "-", "\[Mu]"}], 
          RowBox[{"2", "\[Alpha]"}]], 
         StyleBox["P", "TI"]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "N_{2,3}^*=\\frac{\\alpha-\\mu}{2\\alpha}P", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "f2246b97-7a1a-8c4d-be59-a1ccb0aa1bdc"],
 " cuando\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SuperscriptBox[
          RowBox[{"(", 
            RowBox[{
              FractionBox[
               RowBox[{"\[Mu]", 
                 StyleBox["P", "TI"]}], "\[Alpha]"], "-", 
              StyleBox["P", "TI"]}], ")"}], "2"], "-", "4", 
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{"\[Mu]", 
            StyleBox["P", "TI"], 
            StyleBox["A", "TI"]}], "\[Alpha]"], "\[LongEqual]", "0"}], 
       TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "(\\frac{\\mu P}{\\alpha}-P)^2-4\\frac{\\mu PA}{\\alpha}}=0", "state" -> 
     "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "aff2d73c-f007-9747-824e-377733c190df"],
 ", \nes decir, \[EAcute]ste es el punto de una bifuraci\[OAcute]n de \
silla-nodo (pues un punto de equilibrio aparece de la nada y se divide en \
dos). Despejando ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       StyleBox["A", "TI"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> "A", 
     "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "8327a16a-c953-7e49-a723-3e28257867a8"],
 " podemos encontrar el punto de bifurcaci\[OAcute]n respecto a ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       StyleBox["A", "TI"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> "A", 
     "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "6bdebc2e-418b-0c4d-ac69-4e34d2664c2b"],
 ":\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["A", "TI"], "\[LongEqual]", 
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{
            SuperscriptBox["\[Mu]", "2"], 
            StyleBox["P", "TI"], "-", "2", "\[Mu]", 
            StyleBox["P", "TI"], "\[Alpha]", "+", 
            SuperscriptBox["\[Alpha]", "2"], 
            StyleBox["P", "TI"]}], 
          RowBox[{"4", "\[Mu]\[Alpha]"}]]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {},
      "input" -> "A=\\frac{\\mu^2P-2\\mu P\\alpha+\\alpha^2P}{4\\mu\\alpha}", 
     "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "e1a7f8ab-77cd-e94d-b70f-75da9aa25bfe"],
 "\nVemos que todos los par\[AAcute]metros est\[AAcute]n involucrados en esta \
igualdad, por lo que todos son bifurcantes. Nos gustar\[IAcute]a saber cu\
\[AAcute]l de los puntos de equilibrio (el que tiene signo m\[AAcute]s o el \
que tiene menos) es el estable y cu\[AAcute]l es el inestable. Sin embargo, \
calcular la estabilidad de \[EAcute]stos es complicado. Contraintuitivamente, \
podemos deducirlo calculando la estabilidad del equilibrio trivial.\nPara \
calcular la estabilidad necesitamos ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["f", "TI"], "\[Prime]"], "(", 
         StyleBox["N", "TI"], ")"}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "f'(N)", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "8d2ae3cf-be13-aa45-b05c-3a4d07dbc74e"],
 ", dada por\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["f", "TI"], "\[Prime]"], 
         RowBox[{"(", 
           StyleBox["N", "TI"], ")"}], "\[LongEqual]", 
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{
            StyleBox["a", "TI"], "\[Alpha]", 
            StyleBox["N", "TI"], 
            RowBox[{"(", 
              RowBox[{
                StyleBox["P", "TI"], "-", 
                StyleBox["N", "TI"]}], ")"}], "-", "\[Alpha]", 
            SuperscriptBox[
             StyleBox["N", "TI"], "2"]}], 
          RowBox[{
            StyleBox["P", "TI"], "(", 
            RowBox[{
              StyleBox["N", "TI"], "+", 
              StyleBox["A", "TI"]}], ")"}]], "-", 
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{"\[Alpha]", 
            SuperscriptBox[
             StyleBox["N", "TI"], "2"], 
            RowBox[{"(", 
              RowBox[{
                StyleBox["P", "TI"], "-", 
                StyleBox["N", "TI"]}], ")"}], 
            StyleBox["P", "TI"]}], 
          RowBox[{
            SuperscriptBox[
             StyleBox["P", "TI"], "2"], 
            SuperscriptBox[
             RowBox[{"(", 
               RowBox[{
                 StyleBox["N", "TI"], "+", 
                 StyleBox["A", "TI"]}], ")"}], "2"]}]], "-", "\[Mu]"}], 
       TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "f'(N)=\\frac{a\\alpha N(P-N)-\\alpha N^2}{P(N+A)}-\\frac{\\alpha \
N^2(P-N)P}{P^2(N+A)^2}-\\mu", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "c7f1bc65-d02c-9742-82b2-6ecbed896294"],
 "\ninmediatamente vemos que \n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["f", "TI"], "\[Prime]"], 
         RowBox[{"(", 
           SubsuperscriptBox[
            StyleBox["N", "TI"], "1", "*"], ")"}], "\[LongEqual]", 
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["f", "TI"], "\[Prime]"], 
         RowBox[{"(", "0", ")"}], "\[LongEqual]", "-", "\[Mu]"}], 
       TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> "f'(N_1^*)=f'(0)=-\\mu", 
     "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "ea384ae8-d593-e14a-9cf6-3159b8e56773"],
 ".\nComo ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|
    "boxes" -> FormBox["\[Mu]", TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "\\mu", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "05c15698-962f-a649-9245-fecd04703371"],
 " es un par\[AAcute]metro positivo, vemos que el cero siempre es estable. \
Recordando que, en un punto de equilibrio estable, la gr\[AAcute]fica del \
espacio fase cruza el eje horizontal de arriba hacia abajo, y vice versa en \
un punto de equilibrio inestable, deducimos que el siguiente punto de \
equilibrio despu\[EAcute]s del cero es inestable, y el que le sigue es \
estable (piensa porqu\[EAcute], tiene que ver con la continuidad de ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["f", "TI"], "(", 
         StyleBox["N", "TI"], ")"}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "f(N)", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "6cb397fe-64c3-ff4e-ba72-94ac0ef646db"],
 ", que es continua para todo ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["N", "TI"], "\[NotEqual]", "-", 
         StyleBox["A", "TI"]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "N\\neq -A", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "03b3ba26-9c8a-dd46-87e7-ec8ce9063b12"],
 ", lo cual siempre se cumple porque no hay n\[UAcute]meros negativos de \
personas). Deducimos entonces que \n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SubsuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["N", "TI"], "2", "*"], "\[LongEqual]", 
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{
            StyleBox["P", "TI"], "-", 
            FractionBox[
             RowBox[{"\[Mu]", 
               StyleBox["P", "TI"]}], "\[Alpha]"], "-", 
            SqrtBox[
             RowBox[{
               SuperscriptBox[
                RowBox[{"(", 
                  RowBox[{
                    FractionBox[
                    RowBox[{"\[Mu]", 
                    StyleBox["P", "TI"]}], "\[Alpha]"], "-", 
                    StyleBox["P", "TI"]}], ")"}], "2"], "-", "4", 
               FractionBox[
                RowBox[{"\[Mu]", 
                  StyleBox["P", "TI"], 
                  StyleBox["A", "TI"]}], "\[Alpha]"]}]]}], "2"]}], 
       TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "N_{2}^*=\\frac{P-\\frac{\\mu P}{\\alpha}-\\sqrt{(\\frac{\\mu \
P}{\\alpha}-P)^2-4\\frac{\\mu PA}{\\alpha}}}{2}", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "db0d821b-7cde-5a4b-96ce-23f7bb019998"],
 " es inestable y\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SubsuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["N", "TI"], "3", "*"], "\[LongEqual]", 
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{
            StyleBox["P", "TI"], "-", 
            FractionBox[
             RowBox[{"\[Mu]", 
               StyleBox["P", "TI"]}], "\[Alpha]"], "+", 
            SqrtBox[
             RowBox[{
               SuperscriptBox[
                RowBox[{"(", 
                  RowBox[{
                    FractionBox[
                    RowBox[{"\[Mu]", 
                    StyleBox["P", "TI"]}], "\[Alpha]"], "-", 
                    StyleBox["P", "TI"]}], ")"}], "2"], "-", "4", 
               FractionBox[
                RowBox[{"\[Mu]", 
                  StyleBox["P", "TI"], 
                  StyleBox["A", "TI"]}], "\[Alpha]"]}]]}], "2"]}], 
       TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "N_{3}^*=\\frac{P-\\frac{\\mu P}{\\alpha}+\\sqrt{(\\frac{\\mu \
P}{\\alpha}-P)^2-4\\frac{\\mu PA}{\\alpha}}}{2}", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "34cc7574-ad4d-6f4a-a84a-35a92e9c7aee"],
 " es estable.\nFinalmente, podemos responder las preguntas que nos hicimos \
anteriormente.\n1) Dado que antes de la bifurcaci\[OAcute]n, i.e. para ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["A", "TI"], ">", 
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{
            SuperscriptBox["\[Mu]", "2"], 
            StyleBox["P", "TI"], "-", "2", "\[Mu]", 
            StyleBox["P", "TI"], "\[Alpha]", "+", 
            SuperscriptBox["\[Alpha]", "2"], 
            StyleBox["P", "TI"]}], 
          RowBox[{"4", "\[Mu]\[Alpha]"}]]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {},
      "input" -> "A>\\frac{\\mu^2P-2\\mu P\\alpha+\\alpha^2P}{4\\mu\\alpha}", 
     "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "d5acfa42-6537-1342-98db-7ae6ef84b2b0"],
 ", el \[UAcute]nico punto de equilibrio que existe es ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["N", "TI"], "\[LongEqual]", "0"}], TraditionalForm], 
     "errors" -> {}, "input" -> "N=0", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "e115601f-4e26-9b4d-ba3a-a10239555a50"],
 " y es estable, entonces s\[OAcute]lo superando esta condici\[OAcute]n el \
movimiento puede sobrevivir. \n2) Si se supera la condici\[OAcute]n anterior, \
se necesitan al menos ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       SubsuperscriptBox[
        StyleBox["N", "TI"], "2", "*"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "N_2^*", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "44832043-4693-3d4c-8a4f-767789955f29"],
 " personas que inicien el movimiento, ya que hasta aqu\[IAcute] llega la \
cuenca de atracci\[OAcute]n del cero.\n3) Si las dos condiciones anteriores \
se cumplen, entonces el movimiento sobrevivir\[AAcute] y despu\[EAcute]s de \
mucho tiempo, habremos convencido a un n\[UAcute]mero ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       SubsuperscriptBox[
        StyleBox["N", "TI"], "3", "*"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "N_3^*", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "b1c8c4e3-42f2-8f47-bc9d-371e1a46e1d4"],
 ", pues este es el punto de equilibrio no trivial.\nEs buena idea que \
confirmen estos resultados haciendo experimentos num\[EAcute]ricos en la \
parta de debajo:"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.948482834840353*^9, 3.948482867317444*^9}, {
